{"tid":1212423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要！幫手send email俾cnn知警察打記者！","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:31:44.000Z","uid":259456,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7f43231a42adf753a675f482cbd7b984358dfeef","tid":1212423,"uid":259456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"之前見到有個post話cnn要警察打記者個段商業新聞既片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同朋友夾手夾腳加左英文字幕同打埋email format<br />\n如果有咩錯麻煩各位巴絲補充同指證<br />\n同時send埋email俾cnn嗰邊同dm佢地啲記者啊<br />\n最後請咁多位巴絲傳開同幫手推一推！<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家加油！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OBvasPUwGOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOBvasPUwGOE&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=1cd312e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OBvasPUwGOE</a>"},{"pid":"8c6b467383a6871caf433cfaf27ee0bf4098625b","tid":1212423,"uid":259456,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:37:46.000Z","msg":"條片始終唔係我既, 我驚遲啲youtube會del<br />\n所以咁多位巴絲最好下載落尼"},{"pid":"0ab50b947bc6d31e1a76a0720cb596df7912362d","tid":1212423,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:37:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"26251c0cfa05f93a86779f183b2bbd07a2f574f3","tid":1212423,"uid":259456,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"Dear editor,<br />\n<br />\nIt was suspected by CNN that  the police used force during the protest. Here is the evidence. <br />\n<br />\nOne of the organization in the HK media industry, Commercial Radio Hong Kong News (CRHKNEWS) , has recorded a video which proves that the police used violence to anyone regardless their identity , such as reporters. The link of the post and video are as follow.<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/crhknews/videos/2420096214722357/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fcrhknews%2Fvideos%2F2420096214722357%2F&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=073e3805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/crhknews/videos/2420096214722357/</a>  <br />\nThe translation of the caption:<br />\n警方晚上在金鐘正義路驅散示威者期間，本台記者在採訪期間多次表明身份，受警員多次推撞，記者並無大礙。    <br />\n While the police were dispersing protesters at Justice Drive at Admiralty, our reporters had been  stating their identity repeatedly ,but were still pushed and confronted by the police for several times. The reporter is safe now. <br />\n<br />\nThe attached video (with subtitles) posted by CRHK NEWS on facebook shows the conversation between the police, protesters and reporters.<br />\n<br />\nHope it is useful for you to reveal the truth.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,"},{"pid":"7d1a54664f62493d1768a352c9902852c629002a","tid":1212423,"uid":259456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"26251c0cfa05f93a86779f183b2bbd07a2f574f3","tid":1212423,"uid":259456,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"Dear editor,<br />\n<br />\nIt was suspected by CNN that  the police used force during the protest. Here is the evidence. <br />\n<br />\nOne of the organization in the HK media industry, Commercial Radio Hong Kong News (CRHKNEWS) , has recorded a video which proves that the police used violence to anyone regardless their identity , such as reporters. The link of the post and video are as follow.<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/crhknews/videos/2420096214722357/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fcrhknews%2Fvideos%2F2420096214722357%2F&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=073e3805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/crhknews/videos/2420096214722357/</a>  <br />\nThe translation of the caption:<br />\n警方晚上在金鐘正義路驅散示威者期間，本台記者在採訪期間多次表明身份，受警員多次推撞，記者並無大礙。    <br />\n While the police were dispersing protesters at Justice Drive at Admiralty, our reporters had been  stating their identity repeatedly ,but were still pushed and confronted by the police for several times. The reporter is safe now. <br />\n<br />\nThe attached video (with subtitles) posted by CRHK NEWS on facebook shows the conversation between the police, protesters and reporters.<br />\n<br />\nHope it is useful for you to reveal the truth.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:38:56.000Z","msg":"記住send埋email啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21ac4b440fdc66faacc3f81a7762ca32db03357","tid":1212423,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:39:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=en04neCgs-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Den04neCgs-s&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=4061d5bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=en04neCgs-s</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n關於後續事宜，燒山呢段野講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962482b1a1ddb1465ef626463d20379267ea3206","tid":1212423,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:39:12.000Z","msg":"大家有共識行動，請幫手推<br />\n<br />\n613行動部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"31bc4743f9b205025c17fcb944c9039e1ddb5c87","tid":1212423,"uid":182113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"好波，一定要推"},{"pid":"cb0f2298b4180484061a46900b54b39c3e08da2b","tid":1212423,"uid":259456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"一定要推！等外國傳媒都知咩事 香港先有得救！"},{"pid":"81174a815c84135d4a76c2ad467d2d5588a468a2","tid":1212423,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco